The&amp;nbsp;Amador County Concert Band is comprised of about 50 local volunteer musicians from Amador and surrounding counties and play spring, fall, and Christmas indoor concerts, as well as community outdoor events.
Typical concert locations are: American Legion Post 108, Sutter Creek Amador Senior Center, Jackson Community Church of Pine Grove Sutter Creek Church Of The Nazarene Sutter Creek United Methodist Church
They also perform&amp;nbsp;at band festivals.&amp;nbsp; The band is open to all who play a band instrument and read music and they&amp;nbsp;welcome new members!
&amp;nbsp;
Rehearsals are Monday evenings from 7-9pm at the Amador High School band room in Sutter Creek. Contact Steve Chambers for more information.
