Corinne Moore, South African-born winemaker and owner of Wine Tree Farm, is known for her award-winning Rh&amp;ocirc;ne varietals and blends.

&amp;nbsp;

The&amp;nbsp;tasting room provides a comfortable ambiance for tasting and learning about our wines and the history of the area. &amp;nbsp;

