If you call ahead, you may be able to grab a reservation at Corinne&amp;rsquo;s well-loved and fascinating Wine Blending Class where you&amp;rsquo;ll taste the Rh&amp;ocirc;ne wines that make up Corinne&amp;rsquo;s blends, and create a wine suited to your taste. You&amp;rsquo;ll even take home a bottle!

&amp;nbsp;

